messages.message:
I’m seeing this error in some of the runs for Cypress. It’s affecting tests that opens a build project and waits for the uploader to be not disabled (which is a lot of tests):
```Metronome customer for cypress-org-admin-enterprise-69818_instabase.com (http://cypress-org-admin-enterprise-69818_instabase.com) not found at _callee2$ (webpack-internal:///./lib/src/IBApi/utils/AjaxAsync.ts:198:17) at tryCatch```
From this API call:
```GET https://crafting-cyp--pr-69818-cypress-instabase.instabase.site.sandboxes.run/api/v2/licenses/spend-limit/cypress-org-admin-enterprise-69818_instabase.com?

{
  "message": "Metronome customer for cypress-org-admin-enterprise-69818_instabase.com (http://cypress-org-admin-enterprise-69818_instabase.com) not found"
}```
From this PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/69818) created this morning. @Xindi Xu have you seen this error before?
